    "created_at": "2016-09-06T14:54:37Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-09-06T14:54:37Z",
    "body": "It would be interesting to make this default behavior. I don't think we could use it out of the box in N1 because certain actions, like opening additional windows, cause the app to \"pop\" out of fullscreen or span multiple spaces. (So your application code needs to be aware that it's in fullscreen mode.) Seems like it would likely work for the majority of Electron apps, though.\n"
  },
